{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "9fd27170-d693-4c7f-9cc0-15e256b61552", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9fd27170-d693-4c7f-9cc0-15e256b61552@2.pkg/1772602071938/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602073003", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9fd27170-d693-4c7f-9cc0-15e256b61552@2.pkg/1772602071938/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602073003"}, "identifier": "9fd27170-d693-4c7f-9cc0-15e256b61552", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>A选项：</p>\n\n<p>“打镲（chǎ）”：错误，“打镲”是方言，有开玩笑、捉弄的意思 。</p>\n\n<p>• B选项：“侦缉（qì）”错误，正确读音应为“侦缉（jī）”，“侦缉”指侦查缉捕 ，所以B选项不符合要求。</p>\n\n<p>• D选项：“行头（háng）”错误，正确读音为“行头（xíng）” ，“行头”原指戏曲演员演出时的服装等，后也泛指服装、装备等 ，所以D选项不正确。</p>\n\n<p>综上，注音全对的一项是C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列词语中加点字的注音完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "title": "下列词语中加点字的注音完全正确的一项是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9fd27170-d693-4c7f-9cc0-15e256b61552@2.pkg/item.json?v=1753102137189", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>搭济（jì）打镲（chà）贝勒（lè）雕梁画栋（diāo）</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>窝囊（nɑnɡ）侦缉（qì）账簿（bù）咬牙跺脚（duò）</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>喧哗（huá）拾掇（duo）煞白（shà）骂骂咧咧（liē）</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>行头（hánɡ）忌讳（huì）侍候（shì）商贾名流（ɡǔ）</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>下列词语中加点字的注音完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "5036342747", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "9fd27170-d693-4c7f-9cc0-15e256b61552", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列词语中加点字的注音完全正确的一项是（　　）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>下列词语中加点字的注音完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9fd27170-d693-4c7f-9cc0-15e256b61552@2.pkg/1772602071938/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602073003", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9fd27170-d693-